snippet.title: Mozart's Magic Flute: The Music Game Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Music Games International presents, Mozart's magic flute! The queen of the night has stolen the sun and casted a wicked spell for the world to forever be dark. Mozart is on a mission to save the world from freeing the queen's spell on the sun, and he will receive all the helps he needs to end the queen of the night's spell and bring back the sunlight to the world and bring back the prince and princess back home.






Notice: I do not own the characters, I do not own the music in the game nor I did not make this game. This was made by Music Games International and songs is owned and made by their original creators, author and composers.
